title: Greenwood House 1 bdrm units available WSG included in rent.
posting_body: Greenwood House is a transit oriented apartment building located on Greenwood, within close proximity to bus lines and commuter areas like Northgate Mall and Aurora corridor, giving quick access to and from either the North Seattle suburbs, or busier Ravenna, Greenalke, Wallingford areas.
Close proximity to 15th Avenue, which also runs through Ballard and Interlake area of Seattle.
All units feature a W/D included in each unit, and comes with a parking stall included in rent.
Water Sewer Garbage included in rent,
